com.here.android.mpa.mapping

Enum Map.LayerCategory

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Map.LayerCategory>
      • com.here.android.mpa.mapping.Map.LayerCategory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Map.LayerCategory>
    Enclosing class:
    Map

    public static enum Map.LayerCategory
extends java.lang.Enum<Map.LayerCategory>
    Definition for layer categories within a map. These layer categories can be enabled or disabled dynamically through Map.setVisibleLayers(EnumSet, boolean).
